Owesifazane obedlula ngendlela ngezithuba zabo 8 ekuseni izolo uthe akwaziwa ukuthi isidumbu ngesendoda yakuphi. Uthe usondele ngoba ebona isixuku, wathola ukuthi indoda ibisishonile. “Ubelenga endaweni esobala ebonakalayo ngisho udlula emgwaqweni. Utholakale eseshonile, ngishiye sekukhona ngisho abezimo eziphuthumayo,” kusho owesifazane. Kuthiwa kayikho imizi eduze kwendawo okusolwa ukuthi umufi uzihilele kuyo. Kushaye isikhathi sokuloba amaphoyisa engakayitholi imininingwane ephelele. UColonel Thembeka Mbele okhulumela amaphoyisa uthe owesilisa oneminyaka engu-24 utholwe elenga ngasebhulohweni. Uthe kuphenywa idokodo ngokushona komuntu esiteshini eVerulam.